===Noun===
'''conkers''' (''British; plural and [[uncountable]]'')

#(''plural'') Plural of '''[[conker]]'''.
#(''uncountable'') A game for two players in which the participants each have a [[horse chestnut]] (known as a "conker") suspended from a length of string and take it in turns to strike their opponent's [[conker]] with their own with the object of destroying the's opponent's conker before their own is destroyed.

